VALUES(3008,'NAUGHTY MOTIF RING','66.50 $','3','With its on-trend feather motif and black crystal pavé, it will add a fashionable rose-gold tone plated touch to any day or evening ensemble. Mix and match with other styles to create your own ring party','1');




